				<title>Merry Christmas, Site-19</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1068146/no-one-should-be-alone#post-2186764</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 22 Dec 2014 20:26:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Jacob Conwell</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1372582</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Another Conewell tale. It must be a holiday miracle.</p> <p>This one was written for the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/december-24th-2011-hub">Christmas Collab</a> I was working on with TwistedGears, Roget, FortuneFavorsBold, Doctor Cimmerian, and djkaktus.</p> <p>As you can see, it involves a good chunk of my characters from the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/peregrine-hub">Peregrine</a> series of tales and <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/three-farewells">Three Farewells</a>.</p> <p>Special thanks to djkaktus, TG, Reach, and others for dragging this over the coals.</p> <p>Enjoy the tale, and be sure to check out all the other holiday tales. They are all pretty neat.</p> <p>That is all.</p> <p><em>JC</em></p> 
				 	]]>
